erenden Aneignung zu denken.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 01. Dez 2022) 4aAlterität. 4aBildung. 4aBildungstheorie. 4aDifferenzphilosophie. 4aMedialität. 4aMedienpädagogik. 4aPädagogik. 4aSpur. 4aÄsthetische Bildung. 7aEDUCATION / Research.2bisacsh  aEducation.  aMedia Education.  aPedagogy.  aTheory of Education.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe Gruyterttranscript Backlist eBook Package 2000-2013z978311102523008iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe Gruyterttranscript Highlight Collection Complete Package 2010-2013z9783110352856oZDB-23-TSO08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe Gruyterttranscript Highlight Collection Lit. & Kultur 2010-2013z97831103707440 cprintz978383762121140uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/transcript.9783839421215?locatt=mode:legacy40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783839421215423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783839421215/original  a978-3-11-037074-4  transcript Highlight Collection Lit. & Kultur 2010-2013c2010d2013  a978-3-11-102523-0  transcript Backlist eBook Package 2000-2013c2000d2013  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_SN  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-TSOc2010d2013